INSERT INTO `page_parts` VALUES (1,'body','Fckeditor','<div id=\"gord-cooke-text\">\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h1>WELCOME</h1>\r\n            <p>Welcome to my website that is dedicated to helping the building industry and trade contractors build, renovate and sell more efficient, comfortable, healthier and more durable homes. As a professional engineer, trainer, author and industry consultant for the last 25 years, I have had the pleasure of working with great building professionals across North America who are dedicated to a path of continual improvement. <strong><a href=\"/profile\">Read more</a></strong> <img height=\"7\" width=\"8\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-white.png\" /></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"201\"><img height=\"265\" width=\"201\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/gord-cooke.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"container_home\">\r\n<div><img height=\"235\" width=\"20\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/spacer.gif\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"homebox\">\r\n<div id=\"homebox1\"><img height=\"39\" width=\"259\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/titles/home_cookereport.png\" /><br />\r\n<p>Gord Cooke offers comprehensive seminar and workshop-based training programs to help his clients learn to build and sell better homes. These programs range from a systems approach to building better homes to marketing and selling the key features and benefits of those homes once a company has achieved a high standard of building performance. <span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"/cooke-report\">Read more</a></span> <img height=\"7\" width=\"9\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-black.png\" /></p>\r\n<form id=\"form\" name=\"form\" method=\"post\" action=\"\">\r\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\">\r\n                <p class=\"signup\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 3px;\">Sign-up for our Newsletter</p>\r\n                </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"textfield\" id=\"textfield\" value=\"EMAIL\" style=\"width: 150px;\" /></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"image\" name=\"button\" id=\"button\" value=\"Submit\" src=\"/images/b_submit.gif\" /></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n    </table>\r\n</form>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"homebox2\">\r\n<div class=\"small-side-box\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 9px 12px;\"><img height=\"19\" width=\"151\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/titles/home_upcomming-events.png\" /><br />\r\n<p>EEBA Board Meetings.<br />\r\n<span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"/events/events-calendar\">Read more</a></span> <img height=\"7\" width=\"9\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-black.png\" /></p>\r\n<p>Enbridge Condo Ventilation Seminar.<br />\r\n<span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"/events/events-calendar\">Read more</a></span> <img height=\"7\" width=\"9\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-black.png\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"small-side-box\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 9px 12px;\"><img height=\"16\" width=\"111\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/titles/home_in-the-media.png\" /><br />\r\n<p>Green Building Requirements.. <br />\r\n<span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"/pdf/CondoBusiness%20April%202009.pdf\">Read more</a></span> <img height=\"7\" width=\"9\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-black.png\" /></p>\r\n<p>Stay informed on all of the newsworthy activities.\r\n<span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"/media-room/in-the-news/\">Read more</a></span> <img height=\"7\" width=\"9\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/arrow-black.png\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1),(2,'extended','','',1),(3,'body','','',2),(4,'extended','','',2),(5,'body','Fckeditor','<div id=\"header-inner\"><img height=\"96\" width=\"980\" alt=\"Contact\" src=\"/images/headers/mediaroom.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<p><r:snippet name=\"quick-navigation\"></r:snippet></p>\r\n<div id=\"inner_col-right\">\r\n<h1><img height=\"233\" width=\"169\" align=\"right\" src=\"/images/inner_photos/success-stories.jpg\" alt=\"\" />In the News</h1>\r\n<p>Stay informed on all of the newsworthy activities associated with Gord Cooke and his team of industry-leading building experts and educators. These professionals are in-demand and constantly innovating, so there will always be something new for you to discover here. Check back often.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook Report announcement</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"/pdf/Cook Report announcement_June 17 (Scott).pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Gord Cooke Launches New Training Program and Website for Building Professionals - June 17 </a></p>\r\n</div>',3),(6,'extended','','',3),(7,'body','Fckeditor','<div id=\"header-inner\"><img height=\"96\" width=\"980\" alt=\"Contact\" src=\"/images/headers/mediaroom.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<p><r:snippet name=\"quick-navigation\"></r:snippet></p>\r\n<div id=\"inner_col-right\">\r\n      <h1><img height=\"233\" width=\"169\" align=\"right\" src=\"/images/inner_photos/success-stories.jpg\"/>Articles & Publications</h1>\r\n      <p>Gord Cooke is a regular contributor to a variety of industry publications and writes a monthly column on indoor air quality for HPAC magazine. To access these informative, easy-to-read articles, simply click on the links below.\r\n</p>\r\n      <p><strong><br/>\r\n      HPAC Magazine Articles</strong></p>\r\n      <p> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hpac.sartech.ca/digimag/display.asp?a=278\">IAQ - Working out HVAC Design Details </a><br/>\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hpac.sartech.ca/digimag/display.asp?a=278\"/></p>\r\n      <p> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hpac.sartech.ca/digimag/display.asp?a=10\">IAQ - Hot Time to Sell Efficiency</a><br/>\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hpac.sartech.ca/digimag/display.asp?a=10\"/></p>\r\n      <p> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hpac.sartech.ca/digimag/d